"abhivaḍḍhantī’ti, evarūpaṃ cīvaraṃ sevitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.54:8.8"
msgid "‘Cīvarampāhaṃ, bhikkhave, duvidhena vadāmi—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.54:8.9"
msgid "sevitabbampi asevitabbampī’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.54:8.10"
msgid "iti yaṃ taṃ vuttaṃ, idametaṃ paṭicca vuttaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
